{"tid":1370292,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗搭車車返屋企","createTime":"2019-07-27T02:59:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T03:13:46.000Z","uid":167559,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b01e74027b10156e26d90dbf600343f327ea6e7e","tid":1370292,"uid":167559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:59:39.000Z","msg":"撤退絕對唔可以向元朗西鐵站<br />\n因為 嗰邊畀圍村圍住<br />\n封站嘅話等收皮<br />\n<br />\n撤退向天水圍方向 因為屯門藍地嗰邊都係好多圍村 所以唔建議<br />\n<br />\n天祐苑：<br />\n- 九巴69m 經荃灣 ，終點葵芳站<br />\n- 69x 經美孚、長沙灣、深水埗、旺角、佐敦，終點西九龍高鐵<br />\n- 269B 經西九高鐵站、尖沙咀，終點紅磡<br />\n- 269C 經黃大仙、鑽石山、彩虹、九龍灣，終點觀塘<br />\n-  276a 上水站<br />\n- 城巴 969 西隧去港島，上環至銅鑼灣<br />\n- 龍運 E34A ，東涌及機場<br />\n<br />\n天慈：<br />\n- 九巴265B 經美孚、長沙灣、深水埗、旺角、奧運站，終點柏景灣<br />\n- 269M 經荃灣、葵興、葵芳，終點荔景<br />\n- 276B 經落馬洲皇巴站，終點上水站<br />\n- 龍運 A37 ，直去機場，留意A車比較貴<br />\n<br />\n❌唔好上269D及276P因有機會經元朗<br />\n❌留意，切勿上B1，去福田口岸<br />\n❌鐵巴 K73、K74唔好搭，只去元朗<br />\n❌B2/B2P都唔上得，直接去深圳灣<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n（去天水圍路上，休息站）<br />\n基督教協基會元朗社會服務中心 <br />\n地址：新界元朗水邊圍邨盈水樓平台206-209室<br />\n<br />\n27/7(星期六)<br />\n開放時間定為<br />\n下午2:00-晚上10:00，會按需要延長開放時間<br />\n提供：水，急救物資，食物，情緒支援，休息空間。<br />\n<br />\n是咁的 法官閣下 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/judgehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjudgehk&d=P86Nric8SGsb572WK9RGd7JtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=7640e8b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/judgehk</a><br />\n---------------------------------------------------"},{"pid":"5924f317f9ae93776a91f216f47d9118a8fbffd7","tid":1370292,"uid":144174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T03:01:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6cc5f4d705f4437a28a8ea56dd40ccbf87758b90","tid":1370292,"uid":178013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T03:02:43.000Z","msg":"【小妹文宣出動】多圖  請廣傳  元朗一定要入<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1370271\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1370271</a>"},{"pid":"66de3cac57e109da0bb4ba6abdd4925b5ac6b070","tid":1370292,"uid":178013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T03:03:34.000Z","msg":"【警黑合作極醜惡】小妹整咗「元朗宣言亅，去元朗嘅全部同我入嚟!!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1368803\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1368803</a>"},{"pid":"94c2fc28348a71c8e060e9dcd4ac098939ea4ace","tid":1370292,"uid":143343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T03:05:43.000Z","msg":"朗屏村，朗屏站"},{"pid":"ac27077311057710e92fa9460eb5b0d0107bc682","tid":1370292,"uid":150083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T03:06:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ae2377ba847b896e852bc038dbd3ed4cb5838727","tid":1370292,"uid":51105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T03:13:46.000Z","msg":"天水圍成條廈村喺度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}